<br>
Why?<br>
<br>
Because someone did exactly what this guy did, and a customer complained.  <br>
<br>
When you work customer service, the people on the other side of the counter are your PRIMARY concern.  Anyone on the phone has to wait when someone is standing at the counter, or you hang up and call them back when customers are gone.  That's the reality of working in customer service.<br>
<br>
He was rude.  You were right to call him on it.  I'm sure his manager will be speaking with him when he views the tapes. <p><center><img src="http://www.dreamchaserz.net/crs/completed/sig_kerrib.jpg"><BR><i>~*High Priestess of Luclin, the Maiden of Shadows*~<br>~~~~~~~~~~<br><a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/btheblessedshadowsembrace>Visit the Maiden's Temple</a><br><br><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness>Harvesters of Darkness</a><br><br><a href=http://pub150.ezboard.com/bhamunaptra>Hamunaptra, City of Chaos</a><br>~~~~~~~~~~<BR><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=208851>Garb of a Priestess</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9>OT/OOC Forum</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.31b<br>Copyright ©1999-2004 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  